858
00:49:03,482 --> 00:49:05,317
<font color=#FFFF00>Dan jalan setapak di depan gereja.</font>

859
00:49:05,943 --> 00:49:07,319
<font color=#FFFF00>Juga,</font>

860
00:49:07,611 --> 00:49:08,862
<font color=#FFFF00>Kafe di pantai.</font>

861
00:49:09,279 --> 00:49:10,948
<font color=#FFFF00>Yang terkenal dengan teh hitamnya.</font>

862
00:49:13,534 --> 00:49:15,953
<font color=#FFFF00>Lebih dari 5 wanita pergi
